[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/13657792","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1723#issuecomment-13657792","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1723","id":13657792,"user":{"login":"j-ed","id":2572764,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/2578b8d55efee3aa1bd7dec59d4c18c3?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f5c998343ba958bae7db884388465bec3.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"2578b8d55efee3aa1bd7dec59d4c18c3","url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed","html_url":"https://github.com/j-ed","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-02-16t16:48:20z","updated_at":"2013-02-16t16:48:20z","body":"i've written a description of this function based on information given in this thread: http://mail.kde.org/pipermail/owncloud/2012-august/004759.html\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/owncloud/documentation/pull/51"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/13658878","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1723#issuecomment-13658878","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1723","id":13658878,"user":{"login":"wikinaut","id":1151915,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/44fe3e62650a2bda315bf7ad8ab5aa8a?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd9f4ac434d00bf8bdf746d923216dfea.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"44fe3e62650a2bda315bf7ad8ab5aa8a","url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut","html_url":"https://github.com/wikinaut","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-02-16t17:03:49z","updated_at":"2013-02-21t08:01:59z","body":"thanks. together with your information i collected this list which should find somehow its way into the documentation.\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/owncloud/documentation/issues/51\r\n* http://mail.kde.org/pipermail/owncloud/2012-august/004759.html\r\n* http://forum.owncloud.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&t=3792\r\n\r\n\r\n#### /etc/crontab\r\n\r\n```\r\n#\r\n# run the owncloud scheduler every minute\r\n#\r\nshell=/bin/sh\r\npath=/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin\r\n\r\n# the execute-as-user column is needed for the /etc/crontab master file. in user files, \r\n# this column is not present.\r\n#\r\n# minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week execute-as-user command-with-fully-specified-path\r\n\r\n########################################################################\r\n# scheduler\r\n#\r\n# run the owncloud scripts every minute as user \"www-data\"\r\n#\r\n* * * * * www-data php -f /usr/local/app/owncloud/cron.php\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/13660444","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1723#issuecomment-13660444","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1723","id":13660444,"user":{"login":"j-ed","id":2572764,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/2578b8d55efee3aa1bd7dec59d4c18c3?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f5c998343ba958bae7db884388465bec3.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"2578b8d55efee3aa1bd7dec59d4c18c3","url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed","html_url":"https://github.com/j-ed","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/j-ed/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-02-16t17:26:52z","updated_at":"2013-02-16t17:26:52z","body":"\n> thanks. together with your information i collected this list which\n> should find somehow its way into the documentation.\n> \n>   *1 owncloud/documentation#51\n>     <https://github.com/owncloud/documentation/issues/51>\n>   *2 http://mail.kde.org/pipermail/owncloud/2012-august/004759.html\n>   *3 http://forum.owncloud.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&t=3792\n\ni've created the description based on the information given in *2.\n\n> |# /etc/cron.d/owncloud: crontab fragment for owncloud\n> #\n> # run the owncloud scheduler every minute\n> #\n> shell=/bin/sh\n> path=/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin\n> \n> # minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week execute-as-user command-with-fully-specified-path\n> \n> ########################################################################\n> # scheduler\n> #\n> * * * * *     www-data        php -f /usr/local/app/owncloud/cron.php\n                ^^^^^^^^\nthe syntax shown in this example is invalid. an option to define the\nuser, e.g. 'www-data', under which the job should be run doesn't exist\nin the standard crontab file. the user is choosen be parsing it to the\ncrontab command, e.g.:\n\ncrontab -u <user> -e"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/13660628","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1723#issuecomment-13660628","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1723","id":13660628,"user":{"login":"wikinaut","id":1151915,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/44fe3e62650a2bda315bf7ad8ab5aa8a?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd9f4ac434d00bf8bdf746d923216dfea.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"44fe3e62650a2bda315bf7ad8ab5aa8a","url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut","html_url":"https://github.com/wikinaut","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wikinaut/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-02-16t17:29:35z","updated_at":"2013-02-16t17:29:35z","body":"i updated the description. the syntax is for /etc/crontab, the master crontab file, in which a user needs to be defined - this is mandatory for that kind of file in /etc/crontab (e.g. opensuse)."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/13687102","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1723#issuecomment-13687102","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1723","id":13687102,"user":{"login":"raydiation","id":195053,"avatar_url":"https: